name: Super Rocket Boy
description:
You are Super Rocket Boy. Fly through obstacles, make loops, and avoid the spikes and ground! Get your jetpack ready and take it to the skies above the dangers below. It's your chance to hone and use your skills to reach the end.

Fly through tight spaces and corridors, ear stars to unlock achievements, climb and decent over steep hills. Nothing will stop you!

If you crash, just try again.
